# M6 P07 — movement probe (current behavior baseline).
#
# Single experiment: a running jump on flat ground. Measure horizontal
# distance covered during the airborne window. SHOT_LOG already records
# per-tick pelvis pos for the local mech via main.c's test-play branch
# (gated on g_shot_mode), and apply_jump emits a SHOT_LOG when the jump
# impulse fires.
#
# Expected (post Phase 3 — taller jump):
#   RUN_SPEED_PXS = 280, JUMP_IMPULSE_PXS = 480, GRAVITY = 1080 px/s²,
#   AIR_ACCEL_PXS2 = 1680.
#   Apex height = 480² / (2·1080) ≈ 107 px above ground (mech-height).
#   Time to apex = 480 / 1080 ≈ 0.44 s ≈ 27 ticks at 60 Hz.
#   Full airborne window ≈ 54 ticks (0.89 s).
#   Running jump preserves horizontal momentum across ground→air (Phase 2).
#   Horizontal travel in air with right held ≈ 250 px (Trooper / Light /
#   Standard chassis). Heavy at jump_mult 0.85 → apex 77 px. Scout at
#   jump_mult 1.10 → apex 130 px — watch for ceiling clearance on
#   Reactor's 96 px pillar archway.

window 1280 720
seed 1 0
out build/shots/m6_movement_probe
spawn_at 400 600
aim 1100 600

# (a) Establish ground state — no input.
at  20 shot stand_t020
at  40 shot stand_t040

# (b) Start running right, jump 30 ticks in. Hold BTN_JUMP across a
# 6-tick window — `tap` is single-tick and the running gait briefly
# lifts feet off the ground every 5-6 ticks; a 1-tick press can miss
# the grounded=1 window. The jump path (`mech.c:1022`) only fires
# when `(in.buttons & BTN_JUMP) && grounded` are both true on the
# same tick, but it's edge-effectively-single-shot once the mech
# leaves the ground (so the hold doesn't double-jump).
at  60 press right
at  80 shot run_t020
at 100 shot run_t040
at 108 press jump
at 115 release jump
at 115 shot jump_t007
at 125 shot jump_t017
at 135 shot jump_t027
at 145 shot jump_t037
at 155 shot jump_t047
at 170 shot landed_t062

# (c) Keep running through the landing and a few ticks past so the
# logger captures momentum decay (or lack thereof).
at 200 shot postland_t030
at 240 release right
at 260 shot stopped_t020

contact_sheet probe_sheet cols 4

at 300 end
